transcribed_data: "I feel on top of the world!"
"I can’t stop smiling, this is amazing!"
"I can’t believe how lucky I am!"
"I just want to enjoy every moment!"
"I feel like something bad is going to happen."
"I just want things to get better."
"I’m feeling on top of the world!"
"I can’t shake this feeling of dread."
"I’m completely stunned by what I saw!"
"Why does everything have to go wrong?"
"I can’t believe how unbelievable this is!"
"I’m just going through the motions today."
"I feel on top of the world!"
"I feel like I’ve been holding back tears."
"Why does this always happen to me?"
"I’m really sorry it turned out this way."
"I feel so happy, I can’t stop smiling!"
"I don’t know what to do, I’m scared."
"I can’t shake off this feeling of fear."
"I’m feeling fine, just taking it easy."
"Today is just like any other day."
